---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="home">
    <h1>Curren Iyer</h1>

    <div class="bio">
      <p>Hi, I'm Curren. I'm from Greenwich, CT and currently live in San Francisco.</p>

      <p>I'm on the Product Strategy team at <a href="https://www.netflix.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Netflix</a>, focused on GenAI projects for content production. Prior to Netflix, I was on the Product/AI Ops team at <a href="https://www.ramp.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ramp</a> in NYC. Throughout my career I've enjoyed working at the intersection of technical and GTM teams across different org sizes and verticals — my experience spans SaaS, media, fintech, and some deeptech domains like space and robotics.</p>

      <p>On the personal front, I enjoy running, going to concerts, and volunteering. For 2026 I'm working on a few goals:</p>

      <ol>
        <li>Build a sustainable fitness regimen for the NYC marathon in November. Hit me up on <a href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/14050464" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Strava</a>.</li>
        <li>Allocate time for experimentation, ranging from learning guitar to building side projects.</li>
        <li>Commit to writing more, at least quarterly.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/curren-iyer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
      <span class="sep">·</span>
      <a href="https://x.com/curreniyer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>
      <span class="sep">·</span>
      <a href="mailto:curren.iyer@gmail.com">Email</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .home {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #1e3a5f;
  }

  .bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .bio p, .bio ol {
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #4a4640;
  }

  .bio ol {
    padding-left: 1.4em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .sep {
    color: #c4bdb5;
  }
</style>
